# Purpose

This document serves as the baseline technical reference for the Northwind Health Solutions cybersecurity portfolio. It defines the organization's business operations, infrastructure, technology environment, users, and security architecture. All projects contained within this portfolio are based upon this environment.

-----

# Organization Overview

Organization Name: Northwind Health Solutions (NHS)

Industry: Healthcare

Headquarters: Columbus, Ohio

Regional Clinics: 6

Employees: Approximately 250

Patients Served: Approximately 55,000 annually

